'From Squeak2.9alpha of 17 July 2000 [latest update: #3187] on 18 December 2000 at 5:16:53 pm'!"Change Set:		moveBeforeAddDate:			18 December 2000Author:			Bob Arning- reposition the scroll bar before adding it to scroll pane"!!ScrollPane methodsFor: 'scrolling' stamp: 'RAA 12/18/2000 17:15'!showScrollBar	(submorphs includes: scrollBar) ifTrue: [^self].	self resizeScrollBar.	self privateAddMorph: scrollBar atIndex: 1.	"scrollBar changed."	retractableScrollBar ifFalse: [self resetExtent].! !